des:
Friends, now get latest cricket scores on Alexa.

With our most recently developed Alexa skill named ‘Latest Cricket Scores’, you can get live scores of all the matches.

Just enable this skill on Amazon Alexa App and say “Alexa, Open latest cricket scores”. Alexa will tell you latest and live cricket scores.
